{"tid":1171064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部駐港公署緊急約見德駐港官員　敦促德方守國際法","createTime":"2019-05-25T12:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T13:58:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"173344a68c2d9a6844529312ffa14f0c15c1a8d4","tid":1171064,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港特派員公署說，負責人昨日緊急約見德國駐香港代理總領事施密特，就傳媒報道德國給予香港兩名曾參與旺角暴亂的棄保潛逃分子，提供「難民庇護」一事，向德方提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n公署說，負責人向德方表達強烈不滿和堅決反對，敦促德方恪守國際法和國際關係基本準則，切實尊重香港的法治和司法獨立，認清錯誤，改弦易轍，不得縱容和包庇犯罪分子，不得干預香港事務和中國內政。"},{"pid":"1861a6e689866db8ff800ba3984358597dc9e8e5","tid":1171064,"uid":53062,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"爛仔講國際法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2134788af733cb5315efe2991ec4b8cf2080fafa","tid":1171064,"uid":5499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"做咩干涉人地國家內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時好鍾意咁話人"},{"pid":"16d6a460afec89f0d3a7c68517868479c8cc9908","tid":1171064,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"一年前唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e719fb7dc209ed953c93c29a7986f342d80c05b","tid":1171064,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫粗暴干預他國內政"},{"pid":"fd2325498a73efed3ead8a4e10892708ccde7622","tid":1171064,"uid":5822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"自己需求就叫人守法 唔係就叫人唔好干涉內政 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e0cab7e5b7f96ef02e83e99c96e623799dc8d2","tid":1171064,"uid":1643,"lik